The paper deals with visual object categorization, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The problem of domain adaptation and generalization is a common challenge in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of deep neural networks (cs.CL) and experiments on public benchmarks (cs.MM).
